## 8 Business Logic yang Belum Dikembangkan

### 1. 🔴 Dual Hash System — Data Integrity Risk

| | monitor.py `_make_hash()` | stage4_utils `make_sha256()` |
|---|---|---|
| **Output** | `hexdigest()[:16]` (16 char) | `hexdigest()` (64 char) |
| **Collision risk** | Lebih tinggi (truncated) | Rendah |
| **Fallback tanpa ID** | `instagram\|{owner}\|{text}` | `instagram\|{post_url}\|{text}\|{created_at}` |
| **Lokasi** | [monitor.py:60-70](file:///c:/Documents/KULIAH/SEMESTER%206/PROJECT/PENELITIANPAKKAMAL/SURABAYASAMBAT/surabayasambat_scraper%20instagram/surabayasambat_demo_monitoring/backend/monitor.py#L60-L70) | [stage4_utils.py:22-23](file:///c:/Documents/KULIAH/SEMESTER%206/PROJECT/PENELITIANPAKKAMAL/SURABAYASAMBAT/surabayasambat_scraper%20instagram/surabayasambat_demo_monitoring/backend/stage4_utils.py#L22-L23) |

**Dampak**: Komentar yang sama di-hash berbeda oleh dua jalur → duplikat di dataset akhir tidak terdeteksi.

