### 3. 🔴 Dual Comment Extraction (Schema Mismatch)

| Field | monitor.py `_extract_comment_data()` | process_queue.py `_normalize_comment()` |
|---|---|---|
| hash | `comment_id_hash` (truncated) | `comment_id_hash` (full) |
| post identifier | `post_url` saja | `post_id_hash` + `post_url` + `post_shortcode` |
| source info | ❌ Tidak ada | `source_account` |
| queue info | ❌ Tidak ada | `queue_id`, `scraping_status` |
